LBNlxPFFkhv8IrQ4g&oe=67028A0D"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "Velocity Car Driving - Car Stunt Simulator | Car Drifting Game", "keywords": [], "long_description": "\ud83d\ude97 Velocity Car Driving Simulator - An Exhilarating Adventure!\n\nDive into the world of driving with Velocity Car Driving Simulator. Experience the thrill of car drifting and stunning stunts in addition to serene exploration.\n\n\ud83c\udf04 Key Features:\n\n\ud83d\udee3\ufe0f Dynamic Environments: Explore meticulously crafted landscapes and cities.\n\ud83d\ude97 Realistic Driving Physics: Feel the authenticity of lifelike driving.\n\ud83d\uddfa\ufe0f Open-World Exploration: Roam freely in expansive worlds.\n\ud83d\udd79\ufe0f Intuitive Controls: Easy controls for immersive gameplay.\n\ud83d\ude99 Car Drifting and Stunts: Master thrilling maneuvers for an adrenaline rush.\n\ud83c\udf1f Download now for an unforgettable driving experience!\n\nEscape the ordinary and embrace the excitement of Velocity Car Driving Simulator!", "short_description": "Embark on a thrilling journey in Velocity Car Stunt/Drift Simulator. Experience the rush of exploration, exhilarating drives, and serene relaxation. Master breathtaking car stunts along the way. Get ready for the ultimate driving adventure!"}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://xzsol.com/privacy.html", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "XZ SOlutions", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://xzsol.com/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": null, "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "673385183287495"}, {"id": "394813081514456"}, {"id": "331529188132278"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "NO_MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb":