, "keywords": [], "long_description": "\ud83d\ude97 Velocity Car Driving Simulator - A Tranquil Driving Adventure!\n\nImmerse yourself in the art of driving with Velocity Car Driving Simulator. Unlike traditional racing games, our simulator focuses on delivering a serene and realistic driving experience that allows you to appreciate the beauty of the road.\n\n\ud83c\udf04 Key Features:\n\n\ud83d\udee3\ufe0f Dynamic Environments: Cruise through meticulously designed landscapes and cityscapes.\n\ud83d\ude97 Realistic Driving Physics: Experience lifelike driving physics for a true-to-life sensation.\n\ud83d\uddfa\ufe0f Open-World Exploration: Explore vast open worlds with endless driving possibilities.\n\ud83c\udf05 Day and Night Transitions: Witness the changing landscapes and city lights as you drive through different times of the day.\n\ud83d\udd79\ufe0f Intuitive Controls: Enjoy easy-to-use controls designed for a relaxing and immersive driving experience.\n\ud83d\ude99 Customization and Relaxation:\nVelocity Car Driving Simulator lets you customize your driving experience. Relax, unwind, and enjoy the therapeutic nature of our driving simulator.\n\n\ud83c\udf1f Download now and embark on a tranquil driving journey!\n\nEscape the hustle and bustle of racing and embrace the calm beauty of the road with Velocity Car Driving Simulator.", "short_description": "Explore, drive, and relax in Velocity Car Driving/Drift Simulator."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://xzsol.com/privacy.html", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "XZ SOlutions", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://xzsol.com/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "673385183287495"}, {"id": "394813081514456"}, {"id": "331529188132278"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app